		We offer complimentary alterations on full-price men's suits and Collection apparel in select Ralph Lauren stores.
		<a href="http://stores.RalphLauren.com/promo/store_list.asp?list=24" class="hdNav">Click here</a> for a list of stores that offer these services. Customers must present a copy of their invoice to the
		store for alterations to be made. Alterations may take up 10 days. <a href="
		javascript:void(window.open('/helpdesk/popup_tailor.html','sizechart','dependent=no,hotkeys=no,resizable=no,screenX=0,screenY=0,width=640,height=345,toolbar=no,status=no,menubar=no,scrollbars=yes'))" class="hdNav">Click here</a> to see available alterations and pricing
		schedule.
		<p />
		Complimentary alterations are made only on items purchased at full price (not on sale items). If you have purchased a
		men's suit or women's Collection item on sale and wish to have alterations made, you may visit any of the <a href="http://stores.RalphLauren.com/promo/store_list.asp?list=24" class="hdNav">select
		Ralph Lauren stores</a> that offer these services and pay an alterations fee. <a href="
		javascript:void(window.open('/helpdesk/popup_tailor.html','sizechart','dependent=no,hotkeys=no,resizable=no,screenX=0,screenY=0,width=640,height=345,toolbar=no,status=no,menubar=no,scrollbars=yes'))" class="hdNav">Click here</a> for a complete clothing alteration
		pricing schedule.
		<p />
		If you have additional questions about alterations in our Ralph Lauren stores, contact a customer service representative
		at <b>888-475-7674</b> or e-mail us at <a href="/helpdesk/index.jsp?display=store&amp;subdisplay=contact" class="hdNav">CustomerAssistance@RalphLauren.com</a>.
