			If you have any questions or concerns, please call customer assistance using our toll-free number: <b>888-475-7674</b> or e-mail us at <a href="/helpdesk/index.jsp?display=store&amp;subdisplay=contact" class="hdNav">CustomerAssistance@RalphLauren.com</a>.
